				<div id="post-126" class="post-126 page type-page status-publish hentry">
											<h1 class="entry-title">Contact Us</h1>
					
					<div class="entry-content">
						<p>If you have any questions regarding this site, please email us at the address below, or leave a comment here.</p>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@thehugoawards.org">info@thehugoawards.org</a></p>
<p>Please note that messages left here will be held for moderation as a precaution against comment spam.</p>





																	</div><!-- .entry-content -->
