				<div class="comment-body"><p>To help fill in a few of the blanks&#8230; The 1984 Hugo base was designed by Kathy Sanders. The 1976 Hugo was was designed by Tim Kirk. The 1988 Hugo base was designed by Ned Dameron.</p>
</div>

