				<div class="comment-body"><p>I have been told that my novel, &#8220;Solfleet: The Timeshift Saga, The Call of Duty, Book One of the Excalibur Trilogy&#8221;, published in April 2007, has been nominated for a 2008 Hugo Award. Is there/Will there be a list of nominees available to the public, or can you &#8220;officially&#8221; confirm the nomination for me?</p>
