				<div class="comment-body"><p>Eligability says in one part &#8220;Note that series as a whole are not eligible. For instance, an episode in a TV show may be eligible, but the TV show itself is not. Sequences of comics that form a story arc or volume may be eligible, but the comic series itself is not.&#8221;</p>
