				<div class="comment-body"><p>We&#8217;ve been helped out here by Colin Harris, who has a copy of the 1970 Worldcon Program Book, which, as he says, &#8220;It lists Hugo Award Banquet at Heidelberg Castle on Sunday evening (Aug 23) at 7.30 p.m, under Toastmaster John Brunner.&#8221;</p>
<p>The banquet would have been followed by the awards ceremony itself, so it would have been sometime that evening.</p>
